<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; }
    .container {
      max-width: 100%;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .container p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container h2 { font-size: 16px; }
      .container p { font-size: 13px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>여기에 공통 컴포넌트 내용</h2>
    <p>이 내용은 모든 상품 상세페이지에 동일하게 표시됩니다.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
